:Diamond::

She looked at him and layed down on the table.  She knew better than 
to trust any bot. Let alone one that would show such kindness to a 
stranger.  She hissed slightly and looked around, studing the layout 
of where she was.  She had trouble focusing her eyes and her head 
felt like it was being split open.  She put her hands up to her 
temples and groaned slightly. "Hssssss"  She rolled onto her side and 
faced Devilduer,"What are you going to do with me?Hsssss."
